          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Targets were made of GdF3 evaporated on a thin carbon",
                "foil. Three different evaporation processes led to",
                "targets with thickness equal to 69, 45 and 78 mu-g/cm2,",
                "and stoichiometric ratios of fluorine to gadolinium",
                "equal to 2.89, 2.22, 2.17, as evaporation does not",
                "assure the initial stoichiometry equal to 3."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The elastic scattered protons were measured by",
                "surface barrier detector placed at the angle of 165degr"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A Ge(HP) detector, pleaced at 135 degr. to the",
                "beam axis was used to detect the gamma radiation from",
                "19F(p,ag)16O.",
                "The particle detector, situated at 8.25cm from the",
                "target, collimated by an aperture 2.0-mm wide,",
                "subtending a solid angle of 1.83 msr."
              ]
            }
          ],
